About this item

  • Recommended by over 1.2 million travel enthusiasts around the world. This versatile and practical accessory makes it a perfect gift for family, friends or colleagues for any occasion.
  • Satisfaction guaranteed: We stand behind our quality products and offer a 30-day free return policy. Try it out for yourself.
  • Flexible Viewing: Dual joints with 360-degree rotation allow for the best viewing angle, whether you prefer vertical or horizontal orientation.
  • Fits Most Phones: Compatible with a wide range of phone sizes, from the iPhone Mini to the Samsung Note 20 Plus.
  • Versatile Mounting: The strong clamp can attach to tables, luggage handles, gym equipment, and more, up to 1.5 inches wide.
  • Hands-free Convenience: Keep your phone within reach and in sight, whether you're on a plane, at your desk, or working out at the gym.
  • Other uses of this phone holder: video call for work; holding phone for group photo; taking time lapse photographic; filming videos; desktop headphone holder.
  • Please note certain larger phones with thick protective cases might not fit this mount properly. Also, accessories like phone wallets on the back of your phone can interfere with the phone holder's function.

Product description

This universal cell phone clamp holder will be your best travel companion. It is light weight, compact and versatile. Use it as a phone stand, a phone clamp or a handsfree phone holder in flight, at office or just about anywhere you go.

Phone holder opens up to 3 3/4 inches wide. Fitting example: compatible from a bare iPhone mini to an iPhone 12 Pro Max with a protective case.

Clamp opens up to 1 1/2 inches wide. Fitting example: work desk, kitchen cabinet, toddler high chair, wheel chair, window sill, airplane meal tray, gym equipments or even a headset holder.

Some suggestions on where and how to use this holder:

- Kitchen cabinet or island

- Tabletop or night stand

- Airplane table tray

- Bathroom (we don't judge)

- Monitor

- Headphone stand

This product has been patented worldwide including the United States. Patent Date: April 30th, 2019.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.

  • Jacque Osburn
    5.0 out of 5 stars Must have travel accessory
    Reviewed in the United States on 20 June 2025
    Color: multiSize: 1 UnitVerified Purchase
    I bought this Perilogics Universal In-Flight Phone Holder Mount for a long-haul flight, and honestly, I dont know how I ever traveled without it. This tiny gadget made my trip so much more comfortable.

    What I Love:
    Super versatile: It clamps easily onto airplane tray tables, seat pockets, and even luggage handles. Ive also used it at the gym and at my desk.
    Compact and portable: It folds down to about the size of a deck of cardsperfect for carry-ons or even your jacket pocket.
    Fully adjustable: The 360 rotation lets you tilt your phone to any anglegreat for watching movies hands-free or doing video calls.
    Sturdy hold: My phone stayed secure the entire flight, even through turbulence. I used an iPhone 14 Pro with a case and had no issues.
    Things to Note:
    The clamp has a pretty firm grip, which is goodbut make sure you position it before tightening to avoid disturbing the person in front of you.
    It makes a slight clicking sound when adjusting anglesnot a big deal, just something to be aware of in quiet environments.
    If you have a very thick phone case, it may be a tighter fit, but it still works.

    Pro Tips:
    Practice using it at home before your trip. The mechanism is easy, but it helps to get used to the adjustments.
    It also works great on a desk or nightstand if you want to keep your phone upright.

    Final Verdict:

    This mount is a travel essentialsimple, affordable, and incredibly useful. If you watch movies or use your phone for any extended period on a flight, get this. You wont regret it. It also makes a great gift for frequent flyers.
